an application producing

00:42:04.860 --> 00:42:10.980
crazy things to sleep better or
to count your step, whatever.

00:42:10.980 --> 00:42:19.500
I'm sure that there is ways to
restart and to make our memory

00:42:19.500 --> 00:42:20.760
work again.

00:42:23.310 --> 00:42:26.185
I would reflect on these
sort of path if I were you.

00:42:26.185 --> 00:42:27.310
BRICE CHALLAMEL: All right.

